  m_text: '                           5      7

    2) YELLOW ABSENCE RULE

    If
    there are no Yellow wires

    AND the battery count is exactly 3,

    cut the
    top wire (Index 0).


    3) WHITE LEAD RULE

    If the first wire is White

    AND
    the battery count is less than 2,

    cut the bottom wire (Index 4).

'
